OL,3,CChiltern Railways recovers #12,000
OL,4,Cfrom persistent fare dodger
OL,6,FThey should only be issued in
OL,7,Finstances where there were facilities
OL,8,Fto buy a ticket at a passenger's
OL,9,Fdeparture station, and the person
OL,10,Fpassed signs stating the consequences
OL,11,Fof not having a ticket.
OL,13,FIn January 2023, the Department for
OL,14,FTransport increased the cost of the
OL,15,Fpenalty fare to #100, after it was
OL,16,Ffrozen at #20 for more than a decade.
OL,18,FIt is reduced to #50 if paid within 21
OL,19,Fdays.
