OL,3,CChiltern Railways recovers #12,000
OL,4,Cfrom persistent fare dodger
OL,6,FTony Baxter, operations director at
OL,7,FChiltern Railways, said: "The vast
OL,8,Fmajority of our customers pay for
OL,9,Ftheir tickets before they travel but
OL,10,Funfortunately there is still a lot of
OL,11,Fmoney lost on the railway through fare
OL,12,Fevasion every year.
OL,14,F"We are determined to ensure fairness
OL,15,Ffor the paying customer and there is
OL,16,Fno excuse for fare evasion as it has
OL,17,Fnever been simpler to purchase a
OL,18,Fticket.
