OL,3,CChiltern Railways recovers #12,000
OL,4,Cfrom persistent fare dodger
OL,6,F"Anyone risking boarding without
OL,7,Fbuying the correct ticket for their
OL,8,Fjourney is at risk of a penalty fare
OL,9,For prosecution."
OL,11,FIndustry body the Rail Delivery Group
OL,12,Fpreviously estimated that around #240
OL,13,Fmillion is lost through fare evasion
OL,14,Fon Britain's railways each year.
OL,16,FIn January, watchdog Transport Focus
OL,17,Furged all operators in Britain to
OL,18,Fintroduce a so-called yellow card
OL,19,Fsystem, which would mean passengers
OL,20,Fcaught without a ticket being let off
OL,21,Fwith a warning for a first offence.
